        <p>
          There will be five (5) proctored, written exams.  One of the written exams will be a comprehensive final.  All exams are to be independent assessments of your knowledge.  These will be given in CH 301 on campus on dates and times listed elsewhere on the syllabus.  
        </p>
      </li>

